{"id":15115,"date":"2026-04-14T11:07:52","date_gmt":"2026-04-14T15:07:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/?post_type=evenement&#038;p=15115"},"modified":"2026-04-24T09:21:37","modified_gmt":"2026-04-24T13:21:37","slug":"le-marche-des-belles-intentions","status":"publish","type":"evenement","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/evenement\/le-marche-des-belles-intentions\/","title":{"rendered":"Le march\u00e9 des belles intentions"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Le programme <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/programmes\/gestion-et-intervention-en-loisir\/\">Gestion et intervention en loisir<\/a> vous invite au March\u00e9 \u00ab des belles intentions \u00bb.<\/p>\n<div>Vous aurez l\u2019occasion de donner du sens \u00e0 vos cadeaux, notamment pour la f\u00eate des M\u00e8res. Lors de cette journ\u00e9e, plusieurs artisans (produits, nourritures, plantes&#8230;) seront pr\u00e9sents pour vendre leurs produits. L&rsquo;\u00e9quipe de Loisir vous offre la possibilit\u00e9 de gagner des prix surprises avec des billets de tirage.<\/div>\n<div><\/div>\n<div>Ce projet contribue \u00e9galement \u00e0 soutenir financi\u00e8rement le stage au Maroc des \u00e9tudiantes et \u00e9tudiants du programme.<\/div>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":15203,"template":"","categorieevenement":[193,2499],"etiquette-interne":[2287,2317,2328],"class_list":["post-15115","evenement","type-evenement","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","categorieevenement-vie-etudiante","categorieevenement-vente","etiquette-interne-vie-etudiante","etiquette-interne-loisir","etiquette-interne-international"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-04 22:06:12","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"categorieevenement"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/evenement\/15115","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection"